text: The Jacqui Lambie Network (JLN) is a small political party in Tasmania, Australia. It was founded in 2015 by Tasmanian Senator Jacqui Lambie. It is a big tent party. It currently has two seats in the Australian Senate, both being Senators for Tasmania. Category:2015 establishments Category:2010s establishments in Australia Category:Political parties in Tasmania
title: Jacqui Lambie Network
